score as it correlates to
 <em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Relational-Intelligence-Leaders-Influence-Leadership/dp/047043869X/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&s=books&qid=1252890895&sr=8-1" target="_blank">Relational Intelligence</a></em>
 by Steve Saccone.  Your results can offer a picture of what your strengths and weaknesses are in relational
 intelligence.  <br/><br/> In effort to take next steps to grow your personal life, we suggest reading or re-reading the 
 chapters in the book that correlate with the areas of both strength and weakness from your RQ score so that
 you can develop an action plan for growth.  In addition, there are workshops and consulting offered through 
 the book's website: <a href="http://www.relationalintelligence.info">www.relationalintelligence.info</a>
</small></p>

